values:
i have a lump on my forehead... which is fine, i don't mind it, it's more that i don't actually have any memory of hitting my head against anything that worries me.

im sure i did. but when where and how is a mystery. twas almost as bad as the tequila night... (&lt; &lt;

was nice though, ros looked after me and her friends were nice and we all watched anime together ^^ guna go to the cinema later. not sure what we're seeing but shud be fun.

Well I just woke up from a very interesting night out, during which I met some very interesting people, including one from halls who i had heard about a few times but hadnt had the honor of meeting. that was an interesting talk... and quite a scary coincidence to be honest. going out with them again tonight, theres a metal night in town with free entry :D glad we met coz theyre very nice, friendly ppl, who i wierdly enough get on with. so, yay :) but also at the same time confusion.. ^^;
a guy came and danced with me too, which was fun, and it wasnt sleazy it was fun random dancing to manic rock music :D made me laugh :) i like him (as a friend sorta guy obv), i shuda got his number prolly but i wasnt rly thinking.. ^^;

drank way too much last night though. had 3 strong vodka cokes, a tequila shot, a snake bite mixed with a vodka shot, and a JD coke. some marks of how drunk i was are 1) i started dancing on a practically empty dance floor in front of many people, 2) i fell off my chair, 3) I forgot for an instant where i was when i woke up and then didnt know how i got there (still dont), 4) i was lying on the pavement while we were waiting for the bus, using my scarf as a pillow, 5) I found my boots under the kitchen table and I don't know how or when they got there. I told myself i wasnt going out or drinking last night... or tonight actually but i dont see that happening so meh. whatever.

guna go make myself some breakfast. yes, breakfast at 1am, but i dont care, and u cant judge me.
